data.description: Fantastic all one level 4 bedroom 2 bath home with attached garage! Living room with vaulted ceiling & ceiling fan! Kitchen with range, built in microwave, dishwasher, backsplash & breakfast room! Dining room with crown molding & chair rail! Owner suite with tray ceiling, 2 walk in closets, bath with double sink vanity, soaking tub & separate shower! Spacious spare bedrooms, one with vaulted ceiling! Guest bathroom! Laundry room! Patio & privacy fenced backyard! Great location with easy access to Fort Eisenhower, I-520 & more!
